Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.50,0:01:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.04,0:01:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用踢的太卑鄙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.14,0:01:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼呀 我是忍者\N是你自己不該大意輕心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.58,0:02:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我生氣了！\N這次不會手下留情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.34,0:02:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來你還有手下留情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.18,0:02:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.95,0:02:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這邊這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.18,0:02:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.22,0:02:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來小操的功夫比他高一籌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.72,0:02:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我本來以為偶爾與\N其他流派比賽是個好學習…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.36,0:02:17.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他徹底變成鼬鼠姑娘的玩具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.00,0:02:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第八十九話\N我的天使小操  京都派來迎接者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.91,0:02:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.48,0:02:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是實力差別呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.64,0:02:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身為我們神谷道場大弟子\N彌彥 你太不中用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.25,0:02:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少囉唆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.85,0:02:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,流了不少汗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.79,0:02:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了 鼬鼠姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.29,0:02:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想留在這裏到何時啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.83,0:02:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不准喊我鼬鼠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.36,0:02:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都無所謂啦 我喜歡這裏\N可以吧 阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.10,0:02:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想留多久我都沒關係的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.33,0:03:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是小操\N你不回京都真的沒關係嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.01,0:03:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翁爺爺可能會擔心哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.47,0:03:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒那種事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.71,0:03:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他呀 一定趁我不在\N正加緊猛追女孩子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.88,0:03:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那邊的小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.02,0:03:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟我一起喝茶好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.25,0:03:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟老頭 沒品味 土死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.99,0:03:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要 別過來\N喂！等一下呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.73,0:03:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種事有可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.46,0:03:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們那樣說不好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.57,0:03:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該還有一個人\N也在等著小操回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.67,0:03:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒼紫一定很擔心你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.91,0:03:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.85,0:03:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.35,0:03:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是身為御庭番眾的頭目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.75,0:03:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,確實不能老讓京都沒人鎮守\N我得趕快回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.69,0:03:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.72,0:03:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好耶 快點滾回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.36,0:03:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.29,0:03:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要打嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.00,0:04:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那兩人真有精力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.36,0:04:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知是感情好還是感情差呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.17,0:04:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人在嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.97,0:04:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.57,0:04:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那聲音是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.97,0:04:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.08,0:04:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很熟悉的面孔嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.91,0:04:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好久不見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.25,0:04:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小操在貴府叨擾很久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.92,0:04:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿增跟阿近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.72,0:04:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小操 你遲遲沒回來\N大家都好擔心你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.39,0:04:28.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起 我已經打算回家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.42,0:04:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們倆個是來接她的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.46,0:04:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 不只兩個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.53,0:04:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四乃森蒼紫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.60,0:04:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒼紫 你來迎接小操的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.11,0:04:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翁爺爺很擔心 這是他的信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.82,0:04:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.58,0:04:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的天使小操收？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.59,0:04:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你打算玩到什麼時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.52,0:04:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別給緋村他們添麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.96,0:05:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,溫柔的翁爺爺我\N派遣豪華的人馬去接你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.93,0:05:05.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣？高興吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.86,0:05:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼就快點回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.70,0:05:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有 希望你帶\N淺草的烤娃娃回來當禮物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.07,0:05:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼 再見啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.04,0:05:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個糟老頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.34,0:05:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小操 跟我們一起回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.61,0:05:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了\N這樣你就不怕迷路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.78,0:05:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說你自己吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.82,0:05:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.72,0:05:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了 你倆別吵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.29,0:05:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙講得我像路癡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.69,0:05:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你缺乏自覺嘛\N不要吵了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.29,0:05:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.96,0:05:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.86,0:05:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還不想回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.93,0:05:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小操！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.14,0:05:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小操…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.47,0:05:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們正在忙嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.31,0:05:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小惠 歡迎光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.04,0:05:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連狐貍精都出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.18,0:05:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.68,0:06:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還猜是誰呢\N原來是葵屋的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.88,0:06:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上次多謝你們照顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.92,0:06:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪裏哪裏那次您照顧傷患\N幫助我們很多呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.72,0:06:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我謹代翁爺向您道謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.59,0:06:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們太多禮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.70,0:06:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個人還是老樣子很陰暗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.80,0:06:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了 給他喝看看這個\N加入笑茹抽取液的秘藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.94,0:06:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小惠 你又拿出奇怪東西…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.31,0:06:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別站在外面談\N大家都進去裏面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.19,0:06:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小操 你別說任性話了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.82,0:06:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說不回去就是不回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.59,0:06:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小操！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.63,0:06:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別喊我小操 喊頭目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.33,0:06:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼連我也得待在這裏啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.63,0:06:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種時候\N讓女人互相商量比較好嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.60,0:06:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比這種不識趣的男人好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.01,0:06:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走遠一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.44,0:07:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是怎麼了 小操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.48,0:07:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先前還說要馬上回去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.15,0:07:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我以為蒼紫大人來了\N你一定會高興的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.89,0:07:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是翁爺叫他來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.72,0:07:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒼紫大人只是因為\N翁爺叫他來 他才來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.53,0:07:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.09,0:07:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹嘛動手打人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.66,0:07:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是呀 那些女人不知在談什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.50,0:07:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,八成不是什麼好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.17,0:07:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心 你在做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.54,0:07:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我正好在找東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.97,0:07:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找東西？食物嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.41,0:07:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是的 這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.55,0:07:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了 我不感興趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.15,0:07:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也許…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.02,0:07:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒼紫大人不是擔心我才來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.39,0:07:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小操 沒那種事的\N蒼紫一定也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.33,0:07:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是呀 雖然他沒說出口\N但是他真的很在意你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.43,0:07:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.07,0:08:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果你鬧彆扭是因為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.30,0:08:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喜歡的男人\N不是自動自發來迎接的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.64,0:08:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小惠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.21,0:08:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小孩子！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.24,0:08:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道 在蒼紫大人眼中\N我就是個小孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.85,0:08:16.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是呢 我跟他有段交情\N所以能夠瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.52,0:08:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個人不是\N別人講什麼就做什麼的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.82,0:08:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必需他自己\N也有那個意願才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.59,0:08:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊 過去從沒自己出動的蒼紫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.03,0:08:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特別從京都來到東京\N光是這樣就很了不起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.77,0:08:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,經你一說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.14,0:08:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那倒也是哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.97,0:08:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了 小操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.78,0:08:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回去京都好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.15,0:08:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就這麼辦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.08,0:08:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趁小操心意沒變之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.42,0:08:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下\N不用那樣急著回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.49,0:08:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難得來一趟 阿增你們\N也到東京觀光一下嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.86,0:08:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.99,0:08:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對哦 得買禮物給翁爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.53,0:09:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對呀 偶爾讓我們\N女人一起出去買東西也不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.23,0:09:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家決定買禮物給翁爺\N順便到東京觀光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.44,0:09:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼嘛 一下子說不回去\N一下子說要回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.24,0:09:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莫名奇妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.68,0:09:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰說要帶我去淺草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.15,0:09:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,路上小心點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.78,0:09:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.02,0:09:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心 那就麻煩你看家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.82,0:09:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們去好好的玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.76,0:09:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼連我也得一起啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.66,0:09:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係啦 人越多越好玩嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.49,0:09:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這下子總算安靜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.76,0:09:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很可疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.56,0:09:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼可疑…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.67,0:09:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,淺草是東京最熱鬧的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.30,0:09:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰小姐那麼貪吃的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.67,0:09:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定是打算\N只要自己大吃一頓就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.61,0:09:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此\N剛才她們是在商量那件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.01,0:09:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡 那醜八怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.68,0:09:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想怎麼辦 左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.95,0:09:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然是要逮個正著了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.08,0:09:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說的對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.28,0:09:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,追了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.95,0:09:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.15,0:09:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼我們就乖乖地等吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.76,0:10:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我覺得這是\N履行那次約定的好機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.26,0:10:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,約定？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.73,0:10:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在京都時不是約定好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.97,0:10:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將來有天要與我一同飲茶嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.81,0:10:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.61,0:10:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,京都的寺廟很不錯\N但是這兒也蠻熱鬧的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.75,0:10:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.42,0:10:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏最出名的地方是…\N賣甜不辣還是壽司的呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.59,0:10:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.10,0:10:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,願劍心能體會到我的心意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.40,0:10:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望可以\N看到蒼紫大人的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.77,0:10:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望翁爺\N好色的毛病能治好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.07,0:10:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請保佑我\N讓我見到比古清十郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.38,0:11:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請讓那個傻瓜腦袋變聰明\N我看是很難了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.95,0:11:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋 會被發現的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.79,0:11:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法 打噴嚏是止不住的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.19,0:11:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小操你許了什麼原望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.66,0:11:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,秘密啦 阿薰你呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.89,0:11:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的也是秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.33,0:11:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了 總之先吃點東西吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.67,0:11:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,肚子空空會沒力氣買東西的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.18,0:11:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不客氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.02,0:11:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我對茶道不精\N無法分辨茶的溫度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.89,0:11:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是這茶很好喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.59,0:11:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你太誇獎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.36,0:11:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 您不需要謙虛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.50,0:11:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個茶讓人喝了心境祥和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.27,0:11:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而 以糖果當茶點…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.94,0:12:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,實在是因為\N這裏沒有適合的茶點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.38,0:12:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡迎光臨…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.35,0:12:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 我們也進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.69,0:12:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.79,0:12:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要葛粉糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.09,0:12:13.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要紅豆年糕湯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.12,0:12:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我點一碗蜜豆餡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.49,0:12:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要芋頭羊羹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.19,0:12:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要糯米團湯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.90,0:12:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼店 全是女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.80,0:12:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小妙 小燕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.00,0:12:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真巧 你們今天來東京觀光啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.00,0:12:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小妙你呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.27,0:12:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天店裏休息\N我很喜歡吃這裏的丸子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.04,0:12:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吧 小燕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.48,0:12:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是呀 怎麼沒看到彌彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.85,0:12:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天他看家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.15,0:12:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了 難得見面\N我們並桌吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.35,0:12:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.62,0:12:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼連小燕也在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.52,0:12:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們好像是這裏的常客耶\N要怎麼辦呀 彌彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.42,0:12:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先觀察一下情況吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.80,0:13:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒼紫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.74,0:13:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.97,0:13:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你快樂嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.02,0:13:18.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起 再來一份葛粉糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.32,0:13:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰 等等…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.69,0:13:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是控制一點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.63,0:13:26.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是說最近有點胖了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.60,0:13:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,話是這樣沒錯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.16,0:13:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是幸福的肥胖嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.27,0:13:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村煮的飯很好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.20,0:13:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想不久以後她會\N變得跟相撲選手一樣哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.37,0:13:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算是住在一起\N也不能太大意哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.31,0:13:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰的體質本來就容易胖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.71,0:13:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要注意別攝取太多卡洛裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.15,0:13:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,減肥吧 阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.22,0:13:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也為蒼紫大人減肥好了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.19,0:13:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小操 你沒那個必要了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.82,0:13:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為你是幼兒體型嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.46,0:14:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰你好過份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.67,0:14:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿近…阿增…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.67,0:14:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.87,0:14:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我想\N小操以後會更有女人味的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.38,0:14:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對 一定沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.08,0:14:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我16歲時很粗枝大葉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.88,0:14:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小操16歲了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.75,0:14:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我以為一定是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.12,0:14:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都以那種眼神看我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.26,0:14:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過份 沒錯 我的胸部\N比一般的16歲少女平坦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.56,0:14:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有小肚子…\N搞不好是水桶身材
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.76,0:14:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是 說我幼兒體型太過份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.67,0:14:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的身材比一般人好\N所以沒煩惱過這類事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.87,0:14:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但這確實是很近切的問題啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.81,0:14:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我給你一點建議好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.88,0:14:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之先每天喝牛奶吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.71,0:14:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攝取足夠鈣質\N自然能長高 胸部也會變大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.45,0:14:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的嗎？\N其他還有呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.99,0:15:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個嘛…為了促進新陳代謝\N要多運動多流汗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.86,0:15:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了促進血液循環\N洗澡時要按摩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.33,0:15:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣按摩呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.96,0:15:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比如這樣按摩這樣按摩…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.07,0:15:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被人看到的話很丟臉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.07,0:15:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女孩子說到丟臉這句話時\N要擺出這種姿勢才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.41,0:15:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小惠 我們該去買東西了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.01,0:15:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說的也是 對了 小操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.15,0:15:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果先前指示的方法都沒用\N就用我教你的最後手段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.95,0:15:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.92,0:15:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.29,0:15:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,交一個喜歡幼兒體型\N有戀童情結的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.39,0:15:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當男友就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.63,0:15:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(戀童情結）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.83,0:15:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.57,0:15:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小事一樁 不必在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.04,0:15:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個好可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.68,0:15:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.98,0:15:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戴看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.71,0:15:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰 很好看哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.28,0:15:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就買下來好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.65,0:16:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再跟蹤下去沒意義 回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.12,0:16:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小燕 你沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.89,0:16:13.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個男人…阿增！阿近！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.83,0:16:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在做什麼 拔刀齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.53,0:16:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做什麼？當然是洗衣了\N就如你看到的一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.14,0:16:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你常做這種事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.57,0:16:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除了雨天之外\N這是我的每日功課
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.18,0:16:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每日功課？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.21,0:16:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是寄宿這裏的流浪漢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.25,0:16:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然得多撿點事做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.52,0:16:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,洗衣很有趣的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.79,0:16:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍哥哥 來玩啦 來玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.96,0:16:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下 很快就洗好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.43,0:16:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點啦 快點快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.43,0:16:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點嘛 快點嘛\N我們去玩 我們去玩嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.67,0:16:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒼紫大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.64,0:16:59.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到這裏就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.11,0:17:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你逃不掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.84,0:17:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.28,0:17:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若你以為逃得出御庭番眾手中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.45,0:17:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就錯大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.75,0:17:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.92,0:17:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拿回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.79,0:17:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.23,0:17:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,犯人呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.03,0:17:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那邊睡覺\N好了 繼續買東西吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.20,0:17:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個扒手跑哪去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.30,0:17:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助 在這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.24,0:17:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是御庭番眾的忍者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.41,0:17:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 你們在那裏幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.98,0:17:38.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不妙 是警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.81,0:17:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.85,0:17:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麻煩 快逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.72,0:17:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想逃？不要跑！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.72,0:17:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.85,0:17:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些女人…\N我不會放過她們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.26,0:17:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是紙鶴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.70,0:17:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好棒 也折紙鶴給我啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.70,0:18:01.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真意外\N沒想到你這麼會應付小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.27,0:18:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前我常折給小操的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.97,0:18:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好棒好棒好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.81,0:18:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真的很珍惜小操呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.12,0:18:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是上一任頭目\N拜託我照顧她的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.35,0:18:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是這樣而已嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.59,0:18:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小操已經不是小孩子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.27,0:18:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些警察有夠頑固的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.44,0:18:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼我們得這樣逃命呀\N我實在搞不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.02,0:18:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彌彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.79,0:18:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.82,0:18:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於輪到我們上場了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.69,0:18:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對付這種小角色有點不過癮\N但是正好適合散散心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.96,0:18:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你少說大話了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.43,0:19:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.16,0:19:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你覺得黑色與白色哪種好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.67,0:19:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不論哪種他都喜歡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.64,0:19:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.47,0:19:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本來就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.34,0:19:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望能夠合他口味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.84,0:19:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐們 來陪陪我們吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.28,0:19:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由不得你們拒絕哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.35,0:19:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們是剛才的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.28,0:19:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最差勁的小偷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.58,0:19:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最差勁又怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.38,0:19:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要叫你這種流鼻涕的小鬼\N知道輕視大人的後果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.82,0:19:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,流鼻涕？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.76,0:19:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小鬼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.26,0:19:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓開吧 我們沒空陪你們玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.16,0:19:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏也有美女呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.77,0:19:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請別用你的髒手碰我\N細菌會傳染的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.74,0:19:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,細菌？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.61,0:19:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,硬餅真的很硬啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.41,0:19:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這臭女人 大家上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.12,0:19:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,借一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.35,0:20:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別小看我 我16歲了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.90,0:20:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒼紫\N小操他們差不多要回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.30,0:20:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不要順便散步\N去迎接他們呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.71,0:20:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,順便散步嗎…那也好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.28,0:20:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們沒上場機會了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.38,0:20:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來遲一步了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.09,0:20:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.89,0:20:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.69,0:20:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們！又是你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.86,0:20:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊…是剛才的警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.19,0:20:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.36,0:20:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站住…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.06,0:20:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是…無辜的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.07,0:20:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒼紫大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.61,0:20:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.57,0:20:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡迎回來 玩得愉快嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.18,0:20:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.61,0:20:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發生不少事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.21,0:21:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了 留下好回憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.45,0:21:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒼紫大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.29,0:21:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是給你的禮物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.76,0:21:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紙氣球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.36,0:21:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想起以前你曾經送給我\N覺得很懷念 就買了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.03,0:21:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你永遠都沒有改變呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.24,0:21:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒那種事 我已經是大人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.55,0:21:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒼紫大人\N下次我們一起去玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.65,0:21:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等下次有機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.52,0:21:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒼紫給人的感覺不一樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.26,0:21:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人的好與壞\N都隨時在改變的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.30,0:21:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助 彌彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.37,0:21:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.10,0:21:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看你們很累的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.34,0:21:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.14,0:21:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有點累
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.97,0:21:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們倆人很怪耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.61,0:22:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是不是肚子餓了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.14,0:22:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法\N吃這個打起精神來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.75,0:22:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不吃了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.15,0:22:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真難得 肚子疼嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.98,0:22:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.25,0:22:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了 明天回京都吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.02,0:22:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.05,0:22:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忘記買給翁爺的烤娃娃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.13,0:22:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法 明天再去買一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.66,0:22:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.36,0:22:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.36,0:22:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.03,0:22:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不為什麼\N你們不論到哪都會惹出事來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.10,0:22:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這話是什麼意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.20,0:22:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.07,0:22:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.60,0:22:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一定背後幹了什麼 快招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.34,0:22:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我什麼壞事也沒幹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.51,0:22:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,騙人\N好痛…真的我什麼也沒幹呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:05.13,0:25:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,武藏野的大地流血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:07.40,0:25:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古時的魔法陣崩潰時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:10.00,0:25:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白虎之道出現了那個男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:14.34,0:25:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帝都的地圖\N描繪出相剋的風興水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:20.84,0:25:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下集 風水奇襲\N設置的五茫星之謎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:25.25,0:25:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敬請期待

